[Episode 21]

3
00:01:48,560 --> 00:01:49,610
His temperament has always been like this.

4
00:01:49,610 --> 00:01:50,870
Don't take it to heart.

5
00:01:52,310 --> 00:01:53,039
No wonder he

6
00:01:53,039 --> 00:01:54,900
kept harping on your case before.

7
00:01:55,050 --> 00:01:55,920
Now that I've seen him in person,

8
00:01:55,920 --> 00:01:57,180
he's really stubborn.

9
00:01:58,310 --> 00:01:59,039
Big Brother.

10
00:01:59,120 --> 00:01:59,560
Big Brother.

11
00:01:59,560 --> 00:02:00,490
Sister-in-law.

12
00:02:01,710 --> 00:02:03,640
Sister-in-law, you're so pretty.

13
00:02:03,720 --> 00:02:06,750
Big Brother, you indeed have g-great taste.

14
00:02:09,729 --> 00:02:10,910
I'm going out for a while.

15
00:02:10,910 --> 00:02:11,680
Keep an eye on that young master

16
00:02:11,680 --> 00:02:12,410
from Huang Residence inside.

17
00:02:12,410 --> 00:02:13,120
Don't let him get away.

18
00:02:13,120 --> 00:02:14,560
Big Brother, rest...

19
00:02:14,590 --> 00:02:15,400
Shut up.

20
00:02:16,030 --> 00:02:17,280
Rest assured, Big Brother.

21
00:02:17,280 --> 00:02:17,810
Let's go.

22
00:02:22,910 --> 00:02:24,170
Where are we going now?

23
00:02:24,960 --> 00:02:25,520
Among the Six Wonders of Guangping,

24
00:02:25,520 --> 00:02:27,480
there are three places left for us to visit.

25
00:02:27,480 --> 00:02:28,960
The Ancient Matchmaking Tree is the nearest.

26
00:02:28,960 --> 00:02:30,160
Let's go there first.

27
00:02:30,240 --> 00:02:30,710
Okay.

28
00:02:34,150 --> 00:02:34,750
This is it.

29
00:02:37,630 --> 00:02:39,430
So this is the Matchmaking Tree.

30
00:02:41,030 --> 00:02:41,750
Looking at it like this,

31
00:02:41,750 --> 00:02:43,410
it doesn't seem that special.

32
00:02:46,280 --> 00:02:47,190
In this world,

33
00:02:47,560 --> 00:02:49,630
most of the famous landmarks

34
00:02:50,010 --> 00:02:51,120
aren't particularly

35
00:02:51,120 --> 00:02:52,320
special themselves.

36
00:02:52,800 --> 00:02:54,800
What truly makes them famous

37
00:02:54,910 --> 00:02:56,510
are the stories behind them.

38
00:02:58,800 --> 00:03:01,790
It's said that during a military rebellion in the previous dynasty,

39
00:03:01,790 --> 00:03:03,750
the Emperor's most beloved Noble Consort

40
00:03:03,750 --> 00:03:04,960
escaped from the palace

41
00:03:04,960 --> 00:03:05,760
and came here.

42
00:03:05,840 --> 00:03:07,590
On the way, she encountered villains

43
00:03:07,590 --> 00:03:08,850
with evil intentions.

44
00:03:09,240 --> 00:03:11,960
The Noble Consort, who was loyal and unyielding, refused to submit

45
00:03:11,960 --> 00:03:14,020
and took her own life under this tree.

46
00:03:15,000 --> 00:03:16,710
To commemorate the Noble Consort,

47
00:03:16,710 --> 00:03:17,800
the Emperor ordered

48
00:03:17,800 --> 00:03:19,030
a tree to be planted here,

49
00:03:19,030 --> 00:03:20,800
embracing this tree

50
00:03:21,079 --> 00:03:22,540
and intertwining with it.

51
00:03:22,750 --> 00:03:24,010
The two trees embrace,

52
00:03:24,030 --> 00:03:25,490
with their roots intertwined

53
00:03:25,490 --> 00:03:27,030
and their branches and leaves intermingled.

54
00:03:27,030 --> 00:03:28,360
The commoners believed

55
00:03:28,560 --> 00:03:29,150
that it was the love between

56
00:03:29,150 --> 00:03:30,680
the Emperor and the Noble Consort

57
00:03:30,680 --> 00:03:32,010
that moved the heavens,

58
00:03:32,240 --> 00:03:34,370
so they named it the Matchmaking Tree,

59
00:03:34,800 --> 00:03:36,530
holding it in great reverence.

60
00:03:42,280 --> 00:03:43,410
I didn't expect that

61
00:03:44,630 --> 00:03:46,680
a place where people come to pray for a good marriage

62
00:03:46,680 --> 00:03:47,590
would have such

63
00:03:47,590 --> 00:03:49,000
a sad story behind it.

64
00:03:50,520 --> 00:03:51,750
This Noble Consort

65
00:03:51,960 --> 00:03:53,760
was truly loyal and unyielding.

66
00:03:55,400 --> 00:03:56,400
You admire her?

67
00:03:58,870 --> 00:03:59,840
Don't you?

68
00:04:03,360 --> 00:04:04,240
I don't know.

69
00:04:05,150 --> 00:04:06,240
I only know that

70
00:04:06,400 --> 00:04:08,000
life is extremely precious.

71
00:04:08,710 --> 00:04:10,750
No matter what happens,

72
00:04:11,030 --> 00:04:13,090
and no matter what problems you encounter,

73
00:04:13,090 --> 00:04:14,630
you should never easily give up

74
00:04:14,630 --> 00:04:15,430
your life.

75
00:04:16,360 --> 00:04:17,920
Why are you so familiar

76
00:04:17,940 --> 00:04:19,070
with this place?

77
00:04:20,829 --> 00:04:22,560
This painting is of Guangping.

78
00:04:22,630 --> 00:04:24,070
I grew up here since childhood,

79
00:04:24,070 --> 00:04:25,930
so of course I'm familiar with it.

80
00:04:28,630 --> 00:04:30,890
So, have you been here with someone else?

81
00:04:34,240 --> 00:04:35,360
I mean, have you ever come here

82
00:04:35,360 --> 00:04:37,890
with someone else to pray for a good marriage?

83
00:04:38,390 --> 00:04:39,190
No, I haven't.

84
00:04:42,850 --> 00:04:43,800
That's good.

85
00:04:49,480 --> 00:04:50,510
What are these?

86
00:04:55,360 --> 00:04:56,830
These are wishing plaques,

87
00:04:56,830 --> 00:04:58,159
used for making wishes.

88
00:05:01,600 --> 00:05:03,000
Do you want to make a wish?

89
00:05:06,620 --> 00:05:08,500
This whole world is fake.

90
00:05:08,950 --> 00:05:10,680
Can wishes made here come true?

91
00:05:14,870 --> 00:05:16,130
It doesn't hurt to try.

92
00:05:23,690 --> 00:05:24,250
Here.

93
00:05:26,370 --> 00:05:29,020
[Safe]

94
00:05:52,040 --> 00:05:53,440
What should I do, Xuanye?

95
00:05:53,820 --> 00:05:54,890
I knocked down

96
00:05:54,920 --> 00:05:56,120
someone else's wish.

97
00:06:00,750 --> 00:06:01,360
How am I supposed to

98
00:06:01,290 --> 00:06:03,410
[Stay true to your heart, and things will work out eventually.
Duan Yingheng]

99
00:06:01,360 --> 00:06:02,800
hang it back up?

100
00:06:04,270 --> 00:06:05,510
Where should I hang it?

101
00:06:05,510 --> 00:06:06,120
Banxia.

102
00:06:15,160 --> 00:06:16,350
Duan Yingheng?

103
00:06:18,430 --> 00:06:20,690
This is indeed my father's handwriting.

104
00:06:20,870 --> 00:06:22,870
It means he's also in this painting.

105
00:06:23,080 --> 00:06:24,080
And look, Xuanye,

106
00:06:24,630 --> 00:06:26,830
he remembers his name is Duan Yingheng.

107
00:06:27,920 --> 00:06:29,240
Doesn't that mean

108
00:06:29,310 --> 00:06:30,040
he's trapped in this painting

109
00:06:30,040 --> 00:06:31,160
just like us?

110
00:06:31,800 --> 00:06:33,659
He must be here somewhere, right?

111
00:06:38,710 --> 00:06:40,510
We're finally about to find him.

112
00:06:43,810 --> 00:06:44,680
Esteemed patrons,

113
00:06:44,680 --> 00:06:46,880
are you here to pray for a good marriage?

114
00:06:49,159 --> 00:06:50,159
Young Taoist.

115
00:06:51,120 --> 00:06:52,630
Have you ever seen this person?

116
00:06:52,630 --> 00:06:54,090
His name is Duan Yingheng.

117
00:06:54,870 --> 00:06:55,830
Duan Yingheng?

118
00:06:57,270 --> 00:06:58,400
I've never seen him.

119
00:07:00,630 --> 00:07:01,190
Right.

120
00:07:02,160 --> 00:07:02,850
There are so many people coming and going.

121
00:07:02,850 --> 00:07:05,250
How could you possibly remember everyone?

122
00:07:08,160 --> 00:07:09,000
Young Taoist,

123
00:07:09,390 --> 00:07:10,850
which temple are you from?

124
00:07:10,920 --> 00:07:13,320
Me? I'm from the Sanqing Temple on Mount Yu.

125
00:07:15,730 --> 00:07:17,660
Or maybe I'm from the Bodhi Temple.

126
00:07:19,480 --> 00:07:20,480
The Bodhi Temple?

127
00:07:22,160 --> 00:07:24,120
If it's the Sanqing Temple, it's the Sanqing Temple.

128
00:07:24,120 --> 00:07:25,890
How could you be from the Bodhi Temple as well?

129
00:07:25,890 --> 00:07:27,480
Because I had a dream today.

130
00:07:28,550 --> 00:07:30,720
In that dream, I was a young disciple

131
00:07:30,750 --> 00:07:32,290
of Master Bodhi at the Bodhi Temple

132
00:07:32,290 --> 00:07:34,140
on Mount Bodhi.

133
00:07:34,440 --> 00:07:36,270
That day, my master, Master Bodhi,

134
00:07:36,270 --> 00:07:37,750
set off for Mount Fangyan

135
00:07:37,950 --> 00:07:39,830
to attend the 90th birthday celebration

136
00:07:39,830 --> 00:07:41,270
of the head master of the Fangyan Sect.

137
00:07:41,270 --> 00:07:42,480
But after he left,

138
00:07:42,480 --> 00:07:44,010
he didn't return for a year.

139
00:07:44,070 --> 00:07:45,130
I missed my master,

140
00:07:45,630 --> 00:07:47,400
so I went down the mountain to look for him.

141
00:07:47,400 --> 00:07:49,159
But as soon as I got to Guangping,

142
00:07:49,159 --> 00:07:50,240
I ran out of money.

143
00:07:50,740 --> 00:07:52,800
So I had to enter the city to earn some travel money

144
00:07:52,800 --> 00:07:54,000
by fortune-telling.

145
00:07:55,670 --> 00:07:56,880
But it's just a dream.

146
00:07:57,190 --> 00:07:59,120
It's a dream, yet not a dream.

147
00:08:00,160 --> 00:08:03,090
This is like Zhuangzi dreaming of being a butterfly.

148
00:08:05,430 --> 00:08:07,070
If this really is a dream,

149
00:08:07,120 --> 00:08:08,130
do you hope to be

150
00:08:08,160 --> 00:08:09,830
a young Taoist from the Sanqing Temple

151
00:08:09,830 --> 00:08:11,830
or a disciple from the Bodhi Temple?

152
00:08:11,870 --> 00:08:13,020
It doesn't matter.

153
00:08:13,510 --> 00:08:15,270
I just hope to discard the false and keep the true,

154
00:08:15,270 --> 00:08:17,720
to eliminate the illusory and preserve the real.

155
00:08:17,720 --> 00:08:19,070
Since it's a dream,

156
00:08:19,650 --> 00:08:21,210
how can you distinguish

157
00:08:21,340 --> 00:08:24,270
between truth and falsehood, reality and illusion?

158
00:08:26,850 --> 00:08:29,710
Where this heart finds peace, there lies the truth.

159
00:08:30,840 --> 00:08:33,270
Young Taoist, your words are full of Zen wisdom.

160
00:08:33,270 --> 00:08:34,070
I'm inspired.

161
00:08:35,960 --> 00:08:36,890
You're too kind.

162
00:08:39,630 --> 00:08:40,789
If you don't mind,

163
00:08:41,390 --> 00:08:44,990
could you help this humble Taoist with the first deal of this day?

164
00:08:50,790 --> 00:08:51,720
Is this enough?

165
00:08:53,870 --> 00:08:54,590
Kind lady.

166
00:08:54,910 --> 00:08:55,390
This bracelet

167
00:08:55,390 --> 00:08:57,670
is worth 100 times of fortune telling from me.

168
00:08:57,670 --> 00:08:59,330
The matter I want you to divine

169
00:08:59,600 --> 00:09:00,730
is worth this price.

170
00:09:01,360 --> 00:09:03,960
May I ask what kind of fortune you seek to be told, kind lady?

171
00:09:03,960 --> 00:09:05,220
Family relationship.

172
00:09:11,950 --> 00:09:14,080
Could you please explain the divination to me?

173
00:09:14,080 --> 00:09:16,120
The time of adversity is ending, and good fortune is coming.

174
00:09:16,120 --> 00:09:17,920
Shake off the dust from your body

175
00:09:18,360 --> 00:09:20,360
and get rid of the dark grime on your body.

176
00:09:20,360 --> 00:09:22,480
Especially during the hours of Mao and Yin, which is 5 to 7 am,

177
00:09:22,480 --> 00:09:23,720
good news will come.

178
00:09:24,000 --> 00:09:25,720
By then, the broken mirror will be mended,

179
00:09:25,720 --> 00:09:27,000
and those who are separated

180
00:09:27,000 --> 00:09:28,330
will surely meet again.

181
00:09:30,240 --> 00:09:31,640
Thank you, young Taoist.

182
00:09:32,630 --> 00:09:35,890
Gentleman, is there anything you want me to divine for you?

183
00:09:36,030 --> 00:09:36,510
I don't.

184
00:09:39,660 --> 00:09:41,170
There's a Matchmaking Tree here.

185
00:09:41,170 --> 00:09:42,100
I'll divine

186
00:09:42,130 --> 00:09:44,730
your marital fortune for you then, gentleman.

187
00:09:46,320 --> 00:09:47,450
Please, gentleman.

188
00:10:02,300 --> 00:10:03,840
The mirror is broken, and the wind doesn't cease.

189
00:10:03,840 --> 00:10:05,400
Don't sail against the current.

190
00:10:05,400 --> 00:10:08,260
Gentleman, this divination is very inauspicious.

191
00:10:09,700 --> 00:10:11,210
Don't take what that young Taoist

192
00:10:11,210 --> 00:10:12,530
said just now to heart.

193
00:10:13,020 --> 00:10:14,830
He's young and lacks experience,

194
00:10:14,830 --> 00:10:16,890
so his divination can be inaccurate.

195
00:10:16,960 --> 00:10:18,390
Let's not talk about him anymore.

196
00:10:18,390 --> 00:10:19,150
At least we discovered

197
00:10:19,150 --> 00:10:20,720
your father's handwriting.

198
00:10:20,720 --> 00:10:22,380
That's quite an achievement.

199
00:10:22,720 --> 00:10:23,320
Yes.

200
00:10:23,660 --> 00:10:25,390
As long as we can confirm he's in the painting,

201
00:10:25,390 --> 00:10:27,390
finding him is just a matter of time.

202
00:10:28,910 --> 00:10:30,390
There are two more places to visit.

203
00:10:30,390 --> 00:10:31,850
I'm sure we'll find clues.

204
00:10:33,020 --> 00:10:33,570
If we

205
00:10:33,600 --> 00:10:35,090
can find a way out,

206
00:10:35,450 --> 00:10:36,760
does that mean

207
00:10:36,790 --> 00:10:37,670
the other people

208
00:10:37,670 --> 00:10:39,870
trapped in the painting can get out too?

209
00:10:39,870 --> 00:10:41,510
Then that young Taoist we just met

210
00:10:41,510 --> 00:10:42,480
could return to the Bodhi Temple

211
00:10:42,480 --> 00:10:43,480
to see his master.

212
00:10:46,840 --> 00:10:47,600
Actually,

213
00:10:48,770 --> 00:10:49,650
60 years ago,

214
00:10:50,270 --> 00:10:52,070
there was a flood on Mount Bodhi.

215
00:10:53,320 --> 00:10:55,650
His master and the entire temple

216
00:10:56,220 --> 00:10:58,020
have long since turned to rubble

217
00:10:58,030 --> 00:10:59,030
and disappeared.

218
00:11:01,080 --> 00:11:02,480
Sixty years have passed,

219
00:11:03,260 --> 00:11:04,720
yet he knows nothing of it.

220
00:11:05,930 --> 00:11:08,590
He must have been in the painting for a long time.

221
00:11:09,390 --> 00:11:10,720
The world in this painting

222
00:11:10,720 --> 00:11:11,840
repeats in cycles,

223
00:11:12,390 --> 00:11:13,550
but the time outside

224
00:11:13,570 --> 00:11:14,900
flows on relentlessly.

225
00:11:15,630 --> 00:11:17,890
Once this place collapses and shatters,

226
00:11:18,080 --> 00:11:19,480
he will instantly age

227
00:11:20,440 --> 00:11:21,570
and turn from a child

228
00:11:21,910 --> 00:11:22,870
into an old man.

229
00:11:24,670 --> 00:11:26,130
If that's really the case,

230
00:11:26,650 --> 00:11:27,310
I'm not sure

231
00:11:27,320 --> 00:11:29,520
whether it's better for him to stay here

232
00:11:29,960 --> 00:11:31,320
or to get away.

233
00:11:32,510 --> 00:11:33,870
If he stays here,

234
00:11:34,320 --> 00:11:35,790
at least he still has hope and

235
00:11:35,790 --> 00:11:37,600
something to look forward to every day.

236
00:11:37,600 --> 00:11:39,320
But if he really gets away,

237
00:11:40,150 --> 00:11:42,270
it would be like waking from a long dream to nothing.

238
00:11:42,270 --> 00:11:44,200
His life would already be at its end

239
00:11:44,440 --> 00:11:46,570
before he could experience anything.

240
00:11:54,950 --> 00:11:55,810
Junior Sister?

241
00:11:57,240 --> 00:11:58,700
Go inform Master quickly.

242
00:11:59,550 --> 00:12:00,410
-Hurry!
-Okay.

243
00:12:07,450 --> 00:12:10,300
[Fa'en Temple]

244
00:12:11,620 --> 00:12:12,960
The incense offerings at Fa'en Temple

245
00:12:12,960 --> 00:12:14,290
are really prosperous.

246
00:12:15,200 --> 00:12:16,550
The Emperor believes in Buddhism.

247
00:12:16,550 --> 00:12:17,750
Plus, this place

248
00:12:17,750 --> 00:12:19,210
once witnessed a miracle.

249
00:12:19,270 --> 00:12:20,080
That's why there are

250
00:12:20,080 --> 00:12:21,430
more people coming here.

251
00:12:21,430 --> 00:12:22,630
What kind of miracle?

252
00:12:24,210 --> 00:12:26,060
Years ago, there was a severe drought in Guangping.

253
00:12:26,060 --> 00:12:27,890
Not a drop of rain fell for four consecutive months.

254
00:12:27,890 --> 00:12:29,870
The people's lives were in dire straits.

255
00:12:29,870 --> 00:12:31,030
So the wealthy people in the city,

256
00:12:31,030 --> 00:12:32,790
led by the prefect,

257
00:12:33,750 --> 00:12:35,240
came to Fa'en Temple

258
00:12:35,790 --> 00:12:36,630
on the day of the Flower Festival

259
00:12:36,630 --> 00:12:39,760
to pray for rain before the Guanyin Bodhisattva statue.

260
00:12:40,200 --> 00:12:41,550
Just as the ceremony began,

261
00:12:41,550 --> 00:12:43,150
an odd phenomenon occurred.

262
00:12:43,240 --> 00:12:44,870
The Guanyin Bodhisattva's statue was seen shedding tears,

263
00:12:44,870 --> 00:12:45,930
thunder gathered,

264
00:12:46,410 --> 00:12:48,870
and suddenly a torrential rain poured down.

265
00:12:50,240 --> 00:12:51,570
After that spring rain,

266
00:12:51,960 --> 00:12:53,620
flowers bloomed everywhere.

267
00:12:54,080 --> 00:12:55,320
The commoners believed

268
00:12:55,320 --> 00:12:56,960
it was the compassion of Guanyin Bodhisattva

269
00:12:56,960 --> 00:12:58,560
that brought the sweet rain.

270
00:12:58,630 --> 00:13:00,500
So they designated the Flower Festival

271
00:13:00,500 --> 00:13:01,620
as the Temple Fair Day.

272
00:13:01,620 --> 00:13:02,510
Devout men and women

273
00:13:02,510 --> 00:13:03,570
all come on this day

274
00:13:03,720 --> 00:13:06,850
to Fa'en Temple to offer incense and pray for blessings.

275
00:13:06,960 --> 00:13:08,030
I see.

276
00:13:10,080 --> 00:13:10,600
But don't you think

277
00:13:10,600 --> 00:13:11,410
searching like this

278
00:13:11,410 --> 00:13:12,540
is leading nowhere?

279
00:13:13,430 --> 00:13:14,510
Since my father remembers

280
00:13:14,510 --> 00:13:15,680
his name,

281
00:13:15,720 --> 00:13:17,720
he should remember my voice as well.

282
00:13:17,870 --> 00:13:19,000
Let's shout around.

