466
00:21:44,560 --> 00:21:45,800
I also...

467
00:21:47,800 --> 00:21:49,400
You have difficulty eating,

468
00:21:51,310 --> 00:21:53,040
and you feel anxious and dizzy?

469
00:21:53,230 --> 00:21:53,800
Yes.

470
00:21:56,380 --> 00:21:57,510
