It's delicious.

570
00:26:13,180 --> 00:26:13,880
This is my homemade

571
00:26:13,880 --> 00:26:15,080
pickled vegetables.

572
00:26:15,470 --> 00:26:17,530
It probably doesn't suit your taste.

573
00:26:17,750 --> 00:26:19,350
Here, have a chicken leg.

574
00:26:19,400 --> 00:26:21,070
I bought it from Li's Smoked Meat Shop.

575
00:26:21,070 --> 00:26:22,270
It's very delicious.

576
00:26:22,440 --> 00:26:23,350
It really is.

577
00:26:23,880 --> 00:26:24,880
When I was little,

578
00:26:25,070 --> 00:26:26,240
what I ate most often

579
00:26:26,510 --> 00:26:27,030
was the pickled vegetables

580
00:26:27,030 --> 00:26:28,230
my mother made for me.

581
00:26:29,440 --> 00:26:30,720
Since she passed away,

582
00:26:31,360 --> 00:26:31,930
I haven't

583
00:26:31,960 --> 00:26:33,420
tasted this flavor again.

584
00:26:34,550 --> 00:26:35,310
I see.

585
00:26:36,360 --> 00:26:37,800
If you like it, eat more.

586
00:26:38,030 --> 00:26:39,430
There's more in the kitchen.

587
00:26:39,430 --> 00:26:40,430
If you don't mind,

588
00:26:40,720 --> 00:26:42,580
take some with you when you leave.

589
00:26:43,960 --> 00:26:46,200
Brother, you can take it all.

590
00:26:46,220 --> 00:26:48,150
I don't like it anyway.

591
00:26:50,880 --> 00:26:52,440
He's so clever and adorable.

592
00:26:52,440 --> 00:26:54,270
He'll surely be successful in the future.

593
00:26:54,270 --> 00:26:55,750
He doesn't have to be successful.

594
00:26:55,750 --> 00:26:56,550
I don't have any expectations

595
00:26:56,550 --> 00:26:57,750
for this little brat.

596
00:26:58,310 --> 00:26:59,710
As long as he can pass down

597
00:26:59,790 --> 00:27:00,850
the Ganshan Clinic

598
00:27:01,400 --> 00:27:02,680
and ensure my demon-hunting skills

599
00:27:02,680 --> 00:27:04,340
don't die out, that's enough.

600
00:27:06,440 --> 00:27:07,270
I can tell at a glance

601
00:27:07,270 --> 00:27:08,930
that you're a blessed person.

602
00:27:09,030 --> 00:27:10,640
Not to mention passing the business down,

603
00:27:10,640 --> 00:27:11,440
he might even

604
00:27:11,440 --> 00:27:13,110
surpass you one day.

605
00:27:15,790 --> 00:27:17,510
This young lady sure knows how to talk.

606
00:27:17,510 --> 00:27:18,790
If that's really the case,

607
00:27:18,790 --> 00:27:20,720
I'd wake up from my dream laughing.

608
00:27:21,790 --> 00:27:22,720
But if you laugh,

609
00:27:23,070 --> 00:27:24,030
I might cry.

610
00:27:24,680 --> 00:27:25,700
In this line of work,

611
00:27:25,700 --> 00:27:27,350
it's all about fighting, killing,

612
00:27:27,350 --> 00:27:29,150
and dealing with demons all day.

613
00:27:29,840 --> 00:27:30,440
I don't want

614
00:27:30,440 --> 00:27:31,570
my son to do this job.

615
00:27:32,200 --> 00:27:33,140
If you ask me,

616
00:27:33,510 --> 00:27:35,310
as long as the family is together

617
00:27:35,550 --> 00:27:38,010
and safe, that's better than anything else.

618
00:27:53,040 --> 00:27:55,370
You two just got married recently, right?

619
00:27:55,430 --> 00:27:56,760
We're not married.

620
00:27:56,790 --> 00:27:57,920
We're just friends.

621
00:28:01,020 --> 00:28:02,150
Don't try to fool me.

622
00:28:02,680 --> 00:28:03,680
I can tell.

623
00:28:05,680 --> 00:28:06,960
Tell what?

624
00:28:07,750 --> 00:28:09,070
I can tell that

625
00:28:10,110 --> 00:28:11,570
you two are deeply in love,

626
00:28:11,920 --> 00:28:13,050
and you're a couple.

627
00:28:16,000 --> 00:28:16,680
Anyway,

628
00:28:17,480 --> 00:28:18,880
you definitely like him.

629
00:28:19,650 --> 00:28:20,300
Later,

630
00:28:20,640 --> 00:28:22,100
we left the South Sea.

631
00:28:23,030 --> 00:28:24,110
He's a good guy.

632
00:28:26,590 --> 00:28:27,790
I think so too.

633
00:28:30,330 --> 00:28:31,930
You've been to the South Sea?

634
00:28:33,160 --> 00:28:34,610
My father took me there.

635
00:28:35,550 --> 00:28:37,420
There's a type of demon in the South Sea

636
00:28:37,420 --> 00:28:39,070
called the Dead Leaf Butterfly.

637
00:28:39,070 --> 00:28:41,400
It's huge, with wings like cattail sails.

638
00:28:41,980 --> 00:28:42,850
This demon

639
00:28:42,970 --> 00:28:44,570
is best at weaving illusions

640
00:28:44,710 --> 00:28:46,300
and bewitching people's minds.

641
00:28:46,300 --> 00:28:47,450
The first time my father and I

642
00:28:47,450 --> 00:28:48,790
encountered this demon,

643
00:28:48,790 --> 00:28:49,920
we fell for its trick

644
00:28:50,070 --> 00:28:51,600
and fell into its illusion.

645
00:28:51,760 --> 00:28:53,160
We almost lost our minds.

646
00:28:53,960 --> 00:28:54,960
But fortunately,

647
00:28:55,160 --> 00:28:56,690
in the end, my father woke up

648
00:28:56,780 --> 00:28:58,040
and slayed that demon.

649
00:28:58,840 --> 00:29:01,320
Actually, the illusions in this world,

650
00:29:02,360 --> 00:29:03,830
although they may seem mysterious

651
00:29:03,830 --> 00:29:04,960
and extraordinary,

652
00:29:05,140 --> 00:29:07,140
they all follow the same principle.

653
00:29:07,480 --> 00:29:08,790
As long as you find the right focal point,

654
00:29:08,790 --> 00:29:10,450
they can be easily dispelled.

655
00:29:11,110 --> 00:29:13,000
People trapped in illusions

656
00:29:13,140 --> 00:29:14,550
are like turtles in a jar,

657
00:29:14,780 --> 00:29:15,850
or birds in a cage.

658
00:29:16,030 --> 00:29:18,200
Of course it's hard for them to break free.

659
00:29:18,200 --> 00:29:19,830
But if viewed from the outside,

660
00:29:19,830 --> 00:29:21,630
they're like flowers in a mirror

661
00:29:21,640 --> 00:29:22,960
or reflections in the water.

662
00:29:22,960 --> 00:29:24,020
With a gentle poke,

663
00:29:24,400 --> 00:29:26,200
they'd dissipate like bubbles.

664
00:29:28,160 --> 00:29:29,720
So you mean,

665
00:29:30,000 --> 00:29:31,480
to break the illusion,

666
00:29:31,800 --> 00:29:33,790
we need to attack from both inside and outside?

667
00:29:33,790 --> 00:29:34,850
You could say that.

668
00:29:35,680 --> 00:29:37,920
The focal points can be divided into two types.

669
00:29:37,920 --> 00:29:38,880
One connects

670
00:29:38,900 --> 00:29:41,100
the door between reality and illusion.

671
00:29:41,440 --> 00:29:42,700
By passing through it,

672
00:29:42,790 --> 00:29:44,390
one can escape the illusion.

673
00:29:44,880 --> 00:29:45,930
The other type

674
00:29:46,070 --> 00:29:47,510
is the person who cast the formation.

675
00:29:47,510 --> 00:29:48,570
As long as they die,

676
00:29:48,880 --> 00:29:51,480
the formation will dissipate along with them.

677
00:29:54,000 --> 00:29:55,070
Dad, look!

678
00:29:55,070 --> 00:29:56,460
I've learned

679
00:29:56,640 --> 00:29:58,370
the Bahuang Fist you taught me.

680
00:30:01,590 --> 00:30:02,190
Young man.

681
00:30:02,820 --> 00:30:04,640
This is our family's ancestral  Bahuang Fist.

682
00:30:04,640 --> 00:30:06,500
Would you like to learn it from me?

683
00:30:10,440 --> 00:30:11,000
Sure.

684
00:30:40,830 --> 00:30:42,360
You're in a good mood today.

685
00:30:43,850 --> 00:30:45,240
I practiced a set of fist techniques,

686
00:30:45,240 --> 00:30:46,970
and it made me feel much better.

687
00:30:48,080 --> 00:30:48,720
Why are your parents

688
00:30:48,720 --> 00:30:50,240
in the painting as well?

689
00:30:52,440 --> 00:30:54,000
That demon must have spent

690
00:30:54,030 --> 00:30:55,490
many years painting this.

691
00:30:55,590 --> 00:30:57,120
It painted whatever it saw.

692
00:30:57,370 --> 00:30:58,100
For example,

693
00:30:58,400 --> 00:30:59,840
the Six Wonders of Guangping

694
00:30:59,840 --> 00:31:00,550
couldn't possibly have

695
00:31:00,550 --> 00:31:01,810
taken place in one day,

696
00:31:02,070 --> 00:31:03,480
but since the painter

697
00:31:03,480 --> 00:31:04,720
was deeply impressed,

698
00:31:04,720 --> 00:31:05,850
it painted them all.

699
00:31:07,390 --> 00:31:09,000
But if it could paint,

700
00:31:09,540 --> 00:31:13,140
why did it have to capture living people to put into the painting?

701
00:31:13,240 --> 00:31:15,510
I'm also puzzled by this.

702
00:31:20,270 --> 00:31:20,900
Perhaps

703
00:31:21,270 --> 00:31:22,960
only by meeting the painter in person

704
00:31:22,960 --> 00:31:24,160
can we get the answer.

705
00:31:47,550 --> 00:31:48,160
Let's go.

706
00:32:02,680 --> 00:32:04,070
How are you feeling today?

707
00:32:04,070 --> 00:32:04,800
Much better.

708
00:32:05,950 --> 00:32:07,880
Thank you for taking me in, Master.

709
00:32:08,240 --> 00:32:09,920
Since Mr. Jiu sent you here,

710
00:32:10,210 --> 00:32:11,070
of course Xiaodongtian has no reason

711
00:32:11,070 --> 00:32:12,000
to turn you away.

712
00:32:12,160 --> 00:32:13,860
Just rest and recuperate here.

713
00:32:13,860 --> 00:32:15,190
When you fully recover,

714
00:32:15,380 --> 00:32:17,710
you can find another place to settle down.

715
00:32:32,280 --> 00:32:34,080
Lady, please line up at the back.

716
00:32:44,030 --> 00:32:45,690
I require to see your manager.

717
00:32:49,750 --> 00:32:51,390
I'm here on the orders of the Minister of the Court of Judicial Review,

718
00:32:51,390 --> 00:32:52,950
Lord Song Zhilian,

719
00:32:53,070 --> 00:32:53,750
to investigate

720
00:32:53,750 --> 00:32:56,000
the case of Lord Xin'an's disappearance.

721
00:32:56,000 --> 00:32:57,260
Since you are well-established in the Underground City,

722
00:32:57,260 --> 00:32:59,430
having been doing business here for a long time,

723
00:32:59,430 --> 00:33:00,760
I wonder if you could

724
00:33:00,880 --> 00:33:02,340
provide assistance to me.

725
00:33:02,720 --> 00:33:03,720
Assisting the government with case investigation

726
00:33:03,720 --> 00:33:05,200
is Xiaodongtian's duty.

727
00:33:05,350 --> 00:33:06,510
However, My Lord,

728
00:33:07,160 --> 00:33:08,220
do you have any leads

729
00:33:08,220 --> 00:33:10,280
on where to start the investigation?

730
00:33:12,590 --> 00:33:13,790
Two years ago, Lord Xin'an

731
00:33:13,790 --> 00:33:14,720
came to the Underground City

732
00:33:14,720 --> 00:33:15,780
with an old servant

733
00:33:16,110 --> 00:33:17,250
to see the Living Healer,

734
00:33:17,250 --> 00:33:18,850
Huangfu Bai, for treatment.

735
00:33:19,110 --> 00:33:20,590
According to Huangfu Bai's diagnosis,

736
00:33:20,590 --> 00:33:21,880
he was found to have a blood-borne disease

737
00:33:21,880 --> 00:33:23,240
and didn't have long to live.

738
00:33:23,240 --> 00:33:24,480
However, after that,

739
00:33:24,880 --> 00:33:26,610
he didn't return to the capital

740
00:33:27,000 --> 00:33:29,800
and disappeared in the Underground City instead.

741
00:33:31,680 --> 00:33:32,430
Lord Sima.

742
00:33:32,720 --> 00:33:33,920
With all due respect,

743
00:33:35,110 --> 00:33:36,920
since His Lordship was already terminally ill

744
00:33:36,920 --> 00:33:38,510
and it's been two years,

745
00:33:38,750 --> 00:33:39,680
even if we find him,

746
00:33:39,680 --> 00:33:41,940
he will probably be beyond recognition.

747
00:33:42,720 --> 00:33:44,380
That's not for you to worry about.

748
00:33:44,380 --> 00:33:45,820
You're well aware of

749
00:33:45,980 --> 00:33:47,240
Lord Xin'an's status.

750
00:33:47,240 --> 00:33:49,570
Even if he has unfortunately passed away,

751
00:33:49,770 --> 00:33:51,630
I still want to uncover the truth.

752
00:33:52,880 --> 00:33:53,530
Well...

753
00:33:57,440 --> 00:33:58,030
What?

754
00:34:00,110 --> 00:34:01,170
Don't want to help?

755
00:34:01,830 --> 00:34:02,680
How could I?

756
00:34:03,400 --> 00:34:05,600
I'm just trying to think of a way to help.

757
00:34:06,180 --> 00:34:06,980
I'm wondering

758
00:34:07,350 --> 00:34:09,190
if you have a personal letter from Lord Song?

759
00:34:09,190 --> 00:34:10,000
If you do,

760
00:34:10,030 --> 00:34:10,400
I can take it

761
00:34:10,400 --> 00:34:12,159
to the managers of other trading companies

762
00:34:12,159 --> 00:34:13,230
to have them join forces with me.

763
00:34:13,230 --> 00:34:14,199
This way,

764
00:34:14,230 --> 00:34:15,760
the search would be faster.

765
00:34:20,030 --> 00:34:22,159
So you think my rank isn't high enough.

766
00:34:22,280 --> 00:34:23,409
No, I wouldn't dare.

767
00:34:25,679 --> 00:34:28,000
Is the Grand Secretary of the imperial court high enough for you?

768
00:34:28,000 --> 00:34:29,199
The Grand Secretary?

769
00:34:30,020 --> 00:34:32,020
Let me be straightforward with you.

770
00:34:32,170 --> 00:34:34,030
There's another Chief Constable

771
00:34:34,070 --> 00:34:35,270
who came here with me.

772
00:34:35,480 --> 00:34:36,679
To be honest with you,

773
00:34:37,030 --> 00:34:38,070
he is the Grand Secretary's

774
00:34:38,070 --> 00:34:39,550
future son-in-law.

775
00:34:40,610 --> 00:34:41,969
If anything goes wrong,

776
00:34:42,360 --> 00:34:44,480
not only will you be unable to bear the consequences,

777
00:34:44,480 --> 00:34:45,940
even your boss, the owner,

778
00:34:46,290 --> 00:34:47,750
won't be able to handle it.

779
00:34:48,460 --> 00:34:50,540
May I ask which Grand Secretary it is?

780
00:34:50,880 --> 00:34:53,139
Is this something you can inquire about?

781
00:34:56,150 --> 00:34:57,440
First, a lord,

782
00:34:57,780 --> 00:34:59,980
now the Grand Secretary's son-in-law.

783
00:35:00,150 --> 00:35:01,940
I could ask Lord Song for instructions,

784
00:35:01,940 --> 00:35:02,690
however,

785
00:35:04,190 --> 00:35:05,800
I'm afraid it's not a letter that will be coming,

786
00:35:05,800 --> 00:35:06,600
but soldiers.

787
00:35:08,040 --> 00:35:08,800
By then,

788
00:35:09,140 --> 00:35:10,190
this Underground City

789
00:35:10,190 --> 00:35:11,850
will be thoroughly searched.

790
00:35:12,220 --> 00:35:13,820
If it affects your business,

791
00:35:15,800 --> 00:35:16,360
don't blame me

792
00:35:16,360 --> 00:35:18,090
for not warning you in advance.

793
00:35:20,110 --> 00:35:22,040
Thank you for the warning, My Lord.

794
00:35:31,610 --> 00:35:33,320
The son-in-law of a Grand Secretary?

795
00:35:33,320 --> 00:35:33,920
Yes.

796
00:35:34,820 --> 00:35:36,020
She wouldn't tell me

797
00:35:36,040 --> 00:35:37,140
which Grand Secretary specifically.

798
00:35:37,140 --> 00:35:39,800
I don't know whether what she said is true or not.

799
00:35:41,280 --> 00:35:43,790
What's that judicial commissioner's surname?

800
00:35:43,790 --> 00:35:44,440
Sima.

801
00:35:45,960 --> 00:35:46,920
Sima.

802
00:35:52,000 --> 00:35:52,880
Interesting.

803
00:35:54,490 --> 00:35:55,190
The time for the gate

804
00:35:55,190 --> 00:35:56,480
to Carefree Land to open

805
00:35:56,480 --> 00:35:57,410
is drawing near.

806
00:35:58,280 --> 00:35:59,480
The Underground City

807
00:35:59,650 --> 00:36:01,980
is indeed getting livelier and livelier.

808
00:36:03,550 --> 00:36:05,000
So, Master,

809
00:36:05,630 --> 00:36:06,690
should we help her?

810
00:36:06,760 --> 00:36:08,670
Of course we should help her.

811
00:36:10,190 --> 00:36:10,840
Chunmian.

812
00:36:12,190 --> 00:36:13,710
Assign more people to assist her.

813
00:36:13,710 --> 00:36:14,580
Once she's done with her antics,

814
00:36:14,580 --> 00:36:15,910
she'll leave on her own.

815
00:36:18,230 --> 00:36:20,090
Get rid of her as soon as possible.

816
00:36:20,920 --> 00:36:21,550
Yes.

817
00:36:38,120 --> 00:36:39,050
You said just now

818
00:36:39,070 --> 00:36:41,400
that you studied at Dexin Academy, right?

819
00:36:41,830 --> 00:36:43,030
How is that possible?

820
00:36:43,100 --> 00:36:44,630
Such a prestigious academy

821
00:36:44,630 --> 00:36:46,400
would never accept someone like me.

822
00:36:46,400 --> 00:36:48,330
Then what about that Master Zhang?

823
00:36:48,840 --> 00:36:50,240
There's no Master Zhang.

824
00:36:50,400 --> 00:36:51,710
I was just making it up.

825
00:36:52,640 --> 00:36:53,930
Besides, they took

826
00:36:53,960 --> 00:36:54,820
your bracelet.

827
00:36:55,680 --> 00:36:56,440
No matter where I said

828
00:36:56,440 --> 00:36:57,630
we came from,

829
00:36:57,800 --> 00:36:58,550
they would let us

830
00:36:58,550 --> 00:36:59,750
come in and have a try.

831
00:37:00,150 --> 00:37:01,000
That's true.

832
00:37:03,920 --> 00:37:06,120
So this is the last wonder of Guangping.

833
00:37:06,760 --> 00:37:09,000
But why is the Night Banquet at South Lake

834
00:37:09,000 --> 00:37:11,000
also considered one of the wonders?

835
00:37:11,730 --> 00:37:12,540
It's said that

836
00:37:12,850 --> 00:37:13,560
Lord Xin'an

837
00:37:13,590 --> 00:37:15,390
is the current emperor's uncle.

838
00:37:16,340 --> 00:37:18,210
When they came to this place years ago,

839
00:37:18,210 --> 00:37:20,500
they found it rich in talent and resources.

840
00:37:20,500 --> 00:37:21,830
So they invited poor scholars

841
00:37:21,830 --> 00:37:23,970
from various places to a banquet at the South Lake.

842
00:37:23,970 --> 00:37:25,280
As long as their poems and essays

843
00:37:25,280 --> 00:37:26,890
stood out at the gathering,

844
00:37:27,400 --> 00:37:28,590
they could drink and chat

845
00:37:28,590 --> 00:37:29,590
with Lord Xin'an.

846
00:37:30,630 --> 00:37:31,590
Even better,

847
00:37:32,040 --> 00:37:33,150
in the following year's imperial examination,

848
00:37:33,150 --> 00:37:34,920
they could achieve official ranks.

849
00:37:34,920 --> 00:37:37,650
That's why it became one of Guangping's wonders.

850
00:37:40,900 --> 00:37:42,760
So, do you know how to write poems?

851
00:37:52,400 --> 00:37:53,060
Gentlemen.

852
00:37:54,970 --> 00:37:57,080
I'm Liu Kuo, courtesy name Kefu.

853
00:37:57,110 --> 00:37:58,840
Pleased to meet you.

854
00:37:59,550 --> 00:38:00,480
May I ask

855
00:38:00,710 --> 00:38:02,570
how to address you two gentlemen?

856
00:38:04,430 --> 00:38:05,430
My surname is Jiu.

857
00:38:08,700 --> 00:38:09,660
Duan Yanqiu.

858
00:38:10,360 --> 00:38:11,030
Mr. Duan.

859
00:38:11,710 --> 00:38:12,360
Mr. Jiu.

860
00:38:13,480 --> 00:38:15,190
May I ask where you two are from

861
00:38:15,790 --> 00:38:17,520
and which academy you study at?

862
00:38:17,860 --> 00:38:19,160
We are from Guangping,

863
00:38:19,270 --> 00:38:20,880
and we study at Dexin Academy.

864
00:38:20,880 --> 00:38:21,800
Dexin Academy?

865
00:38:22,430 --> 00:38:23,960
So we are fellow disciples.

866
00:38:23,990 --> 00:38:25,990
No wonder you both look so familiar.

867
00:38:26,280 --> 00:38:27,090
May I ask,

868
00:38:27,380 --> 00:38:29,180
which master do you study under?

869
00:38:30,320 --> 00:38:31,120
Master Zhang.

870
00:38:31,760 --> 00:38:32,890
Master Zhang?

871
00:38:33,880 --> 00:38:35,920
You mean Zhang Maosong, Master Zhang?

872
00:38:35,920 --> 00:38:36,360
Yes.

873
00:38:36,920 --> 00:38:38,030
But hasn't Master Zhang

874
00:38:38,030 --> 00:38:39,400
been bedridden

875
00:38:39,550 --> 00:38:41,030
for a long time?

876
00:38:46,140 --> 00:38:48,060
We are his bedside disciples.

877
00:38:49,440 --> 00:38:50,270
Bedside?

878
00:38:52,920 --> 00:38:54,480
Pardon me for my ignorance.

879
00:38:54,710 --> 00:38:57,110
I've only heard of closed-door disciples.

880
00:39:17,480 --> 00:39:18,230
Mr. Liu.

881
00:39:18,630 --> 00:39:20,160
How long is this time limit?

882
00:39:20,630 --> 00:39:23,360
It counts as long as the incense is still burning.

883
00:39:35,070 --> 00:39:36,600
You know how to write poems?

884
00:39:38,920 --> 00:39:40,460
This Night Banquet at South Lake

885
00:39:40,460 --> 00:39:42,590
took place over a decade ago, right?

886
00:39:43,400 --> 00:39:44,130
Yes, indeed.

887
00:39:45,570 --> 00:39:46,760
Over the past 10 years,

888
00:39:46,760 --> 00:39:48,110
there have been no fewer than

889
00:39:48,110 --> 00:39:49,280
100 widely circulated new poems.

890
00:39:49,280 --> 00:39:50,960
Although I haven't deliberately memorized them,

891
00:39:50,960 --> 00:39:51,590
I could

892
00:39:51,880 --> 00:39:52,360
still recall

893
00:39:52,360 --> 00:39:53,360
two of them.

894
00:39:54,400 --> 00:39:57,060
And they definitely haven't heard them before.

895
00:40:53,720 --> 00:40:54,620
Why are you out?

896
00:41:01,770 --> 00:41:03,300
I'll fight you to the death!

897
00:41:38,860 --> 00:41:39,570
Today,

898
00:41:40,970 --> 00:41:41,920
even if you have to turn Guangping

899
00:41:41,920 --> 00:41:43,000
upside down,

900
00:41:43,280 --> 00:41:44,480
you must find

901
00:41:44,760 --> 00:41:46,840
those two people for me!

902
00:41:47,230 --> 00:41:47,880
Yes!

903
00:41:51,530 --> 00:41:52,710
His Lordship has read

904
00:41:52,710 --> 00:41:54,000
all the poems you wrote.

905
00:41:54,000 --> 00:41:55,000
He is very pleased

906
00:41:55,600 --> 00:41:57,630
and has specially awarded gold, silver, and valuables,

907
00:41:57,630 --> 00:41:58,880
as well as writing brushes, ink, paper, and inkstones

908
00:41:58,880 --> 00:42:00,630
to aid in your studies.

909
00:42:01,030 --> 00:42:03,760
He hopes you all will study extensively, think carefully,

910
00:42:03,760 --> 00:42:05,730
discern clearly, and act diligently.

911
00:42:05,730 --> 00:42:07,410
He also looks forward to seeing you all

912
00:42:07,410 --> 00:42:08,480
in the capital and achieve high honors

913
00:42:08,480 --> 00:42:11,310
in next year's imperial examination.

914
00:42:13,220 --> 00:42:14,430
Thank you, My Lord.

915
00:42:14,900 --> 00:42:15,760
Studying is for

916
00:42:15,920 --> 00:42:17,710
strengthening and revitalizing our country,

917
00:42:17,710 --> 00:42:19,000
and serving as an official is for

918
00:42:19,000 --> 00:42:20,730
ensuring peace for the people.

919
00:42:20,840 --> 00:42:23,670
This is the message bestowed upon you all by His Lordship.

920
00:42:23,670 --> 00:42:26,310
He hopes all of you will bear it in mind.

921
00:42:26,590 --> 00:42:28,030
We will bear it in mind.

922
00:42:29,320 --> 00:42:30,110
My Lord.

923
00:42:35,900 --> 00:42:38,560
Do you think there's anyone else from outside the painting here?

924
00:42:38,560 --> 00:42:39,410
Very likely.

925
00:42:40,190 --> 00:42:41,280
Upon this scene,

926
00:42:41,510 --> 00:42:42,670
and with this mood,

927
00:42:43,010 --> 00:42:45,080
I would like to recite a poem

928
00:42:45,110 --> 00:42:46,570
to present to His Lordship

929
00:42:47,590 --> 00:42:48,710
and everyone here.

930
00:42:51,110 --> 00:42:54,110
Ten years of study by rain-beaten lamplight.

931
00:42:55,020 --> 00:42:58,220
At the top of a hundred-foot pole, watching the tide rise.

932
00:42:58,470 --> 00:43:01,730
A thousand sails finally cross, with ambitions soaring high.

933
00:43:01,730 --> 00:43:05,980
Ten thousand miles of blue waves reflect the red sun.

934
00:43:06,450 --> 00:43:07,590
Bravo! What a great poem!

935
00:43:07,590 --> 00:43:08,670
Wonderful poem! Truly a magnificent piece!

936
00:43:08,670 --> 00:43:09,670
Excellent poem!

937
00:43:10,150 --> 00:43:11,150
What a great poem!

938
00:43:12,050 --> 00:43:13,490
As expected of you, Kefu.

939
00:43:13,670 --> 00:43:16,130
Your literary talent is indeed remarkable.

940
00:43:16,550 --> 00:43:18,200
My skills are not worth mentioning.

941
00:43:18,200 --> 00:43:20,930
There are many talents from humble backgrounds,

942
00:43:21,210 --> 00:43:22,410
such as Mr. Duan here.

943
00:43:23,100 --> 00:43:24,360
Despite his young age,

944
00:43:24,480 --> 00:43:25,830
he's very accomplished at composing poetry,

945
00:43:25,830 --> 00:43:27,510
even better than me.

946
00:43:29,840 --> 00:43:30,270
Me?

947
00:43:31,070 --> 00:43:31,800
Yes, indeed.

948
00:43:32,000 --> 00:43:33,090
I saw Mr. Duan

949
00:43:33,190 --> 00:43:34,360
pick up his brush to compose a poem just now,

950
00:43:34,360 --> 00:43:36,190
and he finished it with just a few strokes,

951
00:43:36,190 --> 00:43:37,800
showing his quick wit.

952
00:43:39,890 --> 00:43:41,120
You're too kind.

953
00:43:43,230 --> 00:43:45,280
Mr. Duan, there's no need to be so modest.

954
00:43:45,280 --> 00:43:47,140
With His Lordship present today,

955
00:43:47,480 --> 00:43:50,080
Mr. Duan, why don't you compose another piece?

956
00:43:50,440 --> 00:43:51,800
That's right, no need to be modest.

957
00:43:51,800 --> 00:43:52,420
Compose another piece. One more.

958
00:43:52,420 --> 00:43:53,550
Compose another piece. One more.

